---
/**
 * About Page
 */
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - Ioodu's Blog" description="Ioodu - AI & Software Engineer specializing in Full Stack Architecture, Frontend Engineering, and AI/ML Applications">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
      <span class="text-cyber-cyan">#</span> About
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Hello, I'm Ioodu</h2>
      <p>
        AI & Software Engineer passionate about building intelligent systems and beautiful user experiences.
        I specialize in <strong>Full Stack Architecture</strong> with a focus on <strong>Frontend Engineering</strong> and <strong>AI/ML Applications</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        With expertise spanning modern web technologies to systems programming, I bridge the gap between
        cutting-edge AI capabilities and production-ready software architecture. I believe in writing code that is
        performant, maintainable, and user-centric.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend Architecture:</strong> Building scalable React applications with TypeScript, Astro, and modern tooling</li>
        <li><strong>AI/ML Integration:</strong> Developing intelligent features using Python, LLMs, and machine learning pipelines</li>
        <li><strong>Full Stack Development:</strong> End-to-end system design from database to user interface</li>
        <li><strong>Systems Programming:</strong> Performance-critical components in Rust and Go</li>
        <li><strong>Developer Experience:</strong> Creating tools and workflows that boost team productivity</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 not-prose mt-4">
        <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-cyber-cyan font-semibold mb-2">Frontend & UI</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">TypeScript · React · Astro · Next.js · Tailwind CSS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-cyber-cyan font-semibold mb-2">AI & Machine Learning</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Python · PyTorch · TensorFlow · LLMs · OpenAI API</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-cyber-cyan font-semibold mb-2">Backend & Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Node.js · Rust · Go · PostgreSQL · Redis</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-cyber-cyan font-semibold mb-2">Cloud & DevOps</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">AWS · Vercel · Cloudflare · Docker · CI/CD</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="mt-8">Areas of Focus</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI-Native Applications:</strong> Building products that leverage LLMs and machine learning at their core</li>
        <li><strong>Developer Tools:</strong> Creating CLI tools, VS Code extensions, and automation workflows</li>
        <li><strong>Performance Engineering:</strong> Optimizing web applications for speed and user experience</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Writing:</strong> Sharing knowledge through documentation, blog posts, and open source</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Philosophy</h2>
      <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-cyber-cyan pl-4 italic">
        "Code is read more often than it is written."
      </blockquote>
      <p>
        I believe in writing clean, well-documented code that tells a story. Whether it's a complex AI pipeline
        or a simple React component, I strive for clarity and maintainability. I'm an advocate for open source
        and enjoy geek aesthetics in both code and design.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact & Links</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/chinadbo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/chinadbo</a></li>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:chinadbo@gmail.com">chinadbo@gmail.com</a></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>About This Blog</h2>
      <p>
        This blog is my digital garden where I share insights on software engineering, AI/ML, productivity,
        and the tools that power my workflow. It's built with <strong>Astro</strong>, <strong>React</strong>, and <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong>,
        deployed on Cloudflare Pages.
      </p>
      <p>
        The theme features a cyberpunk aesthetic with cyan (#00f5ff) accents, reflecting my love for
        technology and forward-thinking design.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
